fields.title: Tiger
fields.description: The tiger is the largest species among the Felidae and classified in the genus Panthera. It is most recognisable for its dark vertical stripes on orangish-brown fur with a lighter underside. It is an apex predator, primarily preying on ungulates such as deer and wild boar.

fields.title: Blue bubble
fields.description: A bubble is a globule of one substance in another, usually gas in a liquid. Due to the Marangoni effect, bubbles may remain intact when they reach the surface of the immersive substance.

fields.title: Basecamp Personal
fields.description: a completely free version of Basecamp designed with freelancers, students, families, and personal projects in mind. Use it for hobbies, weddings, small events, side projects, volunteer gigs, etc.

fields.title: Hexometer
fields.description: Based on AI technology the Hexometer™ hygiene attendant periodically scans over 2800 data points on your website to make sure your digital assets are in pristine condition. It will also give you tips and tricks on how to improve your website’s hygiene.

fields.title: 8b Website Builder
fields.description: Create your website professionally without coding with 8b Website Builder! Based on Google AMP, 8b allows you to build lightning-fast, responsive and Google-friendly website in a matter of minutes. It includes a free HTTPS SSL certificate, much more!

fields.title: Walling
fields.description: Walling gives you a better way to organize and refine your ideas and thoughts. Unlike linear documents, with your ideas side by side, Walling empowers you to step back and get a high level understanding of what you're working on.

fields.title: Startup Handbook
fields.description: A compilation of best practices in building your startup as inspired by the works of the most-respected founders, operators and investors.

fields.title: HeySummit
fields.description: Increase engagement, conversions and revenue for your online summits. HeySummit allows you to organise, promote, and analyse your online summit with ease.

fields.title: Debby App
fields.description: Just tell Debby your balance and next payment date – she will calculate your daily budget and will help you to save money! She can also freeze a certain amount of your budget and save it until later to pay your rent, bills, or other mandatory payments

fields.title: Emoji Maker
fields.description:
Emoji Maker is web a app for generating custom Twitter emojis allowing you to invent the next best emoji 🥳.
It is largely inspired by the emoji mashup bots active on Twitter and an old emoji builder tool that is no longer functioning.

fields.title: Heartcount
fields.description: Are you done with boring surveys that eat up all of your time, and then no one acts on the results? Heartcount is allowing you to give immediate feedback to your manager, team lead or anyone else, by answering three simple questions each Friday.

fields.title: Flock Trips
fields.description: Flock is a service that will help you and your friends easily plan bachelor parties—no more spreadsheets to budget, doodle to get votes on where to go, email to send out the details, text to find out who's in and out, etc. Everything organized in one place.

fields.title: Sympeak
fields.description: Sympeak is a simple tool that translate symbols/images to speech. Works offline!

fields.title: Cocoon
fields.description: Cocoon is a dedicated space for the most important people in your life. You use it with a single group who you want to feel closer with — it's like your home, on your phone.

fields.title: Microsoft Math
fields.description: Microsoft Math solver is a free app that provides help with elementary, middle, and high school math problems leveraging an advanced AI powered math engine. Draw or Scan math problem and instantly get step-by-step explanation, graph, video lectures and more.

fields.title: CoScreen
fields.description: CoScreen is radically focused on highly agile teams. Any window you drag & drop to your extended screen appears on the extended screens of your peers and vice versa. Everyone has their own mouse pointer and can simultaneously interact with any window.

fields.title: Port Manager
fields.description: We've all been there: You fire up a project in your terminal and are interrupted by an obnoxious "EADDRINUSE" message. Well, no more! Port Manager will spare you countless minutes of pointless frustration.

fields.title: Octotree
fields.description: Browser extension that improves GitHub file browsing and code reviewing experience. Available on Chrome, Firefox, Opera and Safari.

fields.title: Pelion
fields.description:
Pelion is a marketplace for mentorship.
Find mentors to advance your career. Pay them now, or when you earn more.

fields.title: Pockethunt
fields.description: Pockethunt is a casual recruitment chat app with less hassle for people who work in a digital world. Our dream is to change the way recruitment is done, making it more casual, fun and fast.

fields.title: AR Pong
fields.description:
Play Beer Pong wherever you want.
Win against your friends or random people using Game Center matchmaking.
Place a cup anywhere in trick shot mode. Try for the longest distance record.
Earn coins while playing to buy more cups, balls, liquids, and tables.

fields.title: Wavecation
fields.description: Wavecation helps surfers of all experience levels find the perfect place to stay within walking distance to their ideal surf break.

fields.title: TrekWeather
fields.description:
TrekWeather is a modern, simplistic website where you can search for specific trails, peaks, and ski areas in Colorado to receive a detailed and pinpointed weather forecast!
Find the forecast for various points along your route!

fields.title: Stock.Gifts
fields.description: Stock.Gifts is a free service for making all your friends investors this holiday season. Shop a library of stocks to find the perfect match, add a note, and send away. Your friend will receive up to $50 in free stock. Brought to you by Public.com.

fields.title: Invisible Line
fields.description: Invisible line is a mini text editor for experimenting a new way to align text: the text is aligned so as to create an invisible vertical line. Enter your text, choose your favorite style and download or share your invisible line!

fields.title: Kegel Coach
fields.description: An independent Watch OS app, Kegel Coach brings you the best on-the- go Kegel experience on your watch. The beautiful app is packed with features to help you do and track Kegel exercises anywhere, anytime without taking out your phone.

fields.title: Panelista
fields.description: The key to success when making things is to involve your target group. Panelista makes it easy to explore needs and try out new ideas.

fields.title: 21Spotlights
fields.description: Take part in an exciting competition where influencers and gamers present their social media channels. You can vote for your favorites, find new social media channels (instagram, twitch, TikTok etc.) or let new influencers and gamers entertain you.

fields.title: Towedo
fields.description: App will pick up a virtual mentor, the same person as you, who will daily help in achieving the goal. Or find an opponent with a similar goal, and arrange a competition between you.

fields.title: Hippidy
fields.description: Hippidy is the only comparison shopping site that is actually built to be user friendly. Hippidy shows price history with 99% accuracy up to 90 days in the past. No ads, no stress — just accurate data and the easiest way to shop and save up to 70% off.

fields.title: Perimeter 81
fields.description: Perimeter 81 is a Zero Trust Network as a Service designed to simplify secure network, cloud and application access for the modern and distributed workforce.

fields.title: Zipnote
fields.description: Need to take a quick note? Then try Zipnote! Just simply open the app and bam! You are already typing your note! The note saves automatically when you exit the app or click the done button. It's easy to take some quick notes with Zipnote.

fields.title: RepuStream
fields.description:
RepuStream helps you turn your existing customer base into publish 5 star testimonials online.
The RepuStream software helps your business become the only logical choice to customers searching for the products and services you offer.

fields.title: Kampsite
fields.description: Kampsite was made with the aim of helping companies engage with their users to build the features and products that their customers actually want.

fields.title: Drawer
fields.description: Drawer is a collection of high-quality, fully customizable Lottie animations & SVG illustrations that will delight your next project.

fields.title: Spark 2.5
fields.description:
We believe that email experience can be effortless, beautiful and collaborative.
You will love your email again.

fields.title: AnonAddy
fields.description:
AnonAddy is an open-source anonymous email forwarding service that protects your real email address from spam by using a different unique email alias for every website. No adverts, analytics or trackers.
You can create unlimited email aliases for free!

fields.title: Heatbox
fields.description:
Heatbox: The self heating lunchbox
Warm and healthy food anywhere, Anytime. Heatbox is a self heating lunchbox that provides a healthy alternative to microwaving, by heating food through a steaming system nutrients stay locked in.

fields.title: Cookt
fields.description:
Heatbox: The self heating lunchbox
Warm and healthy food anywhere, Anytime. Heatbox is a self heating lunchbox that provides a healthy alternative to microwaving, by heating food through a steaming system nutrients stay locked in.

fields.title: Onesaid
fields.description: Onesaid brings people together to share and explore different points of view and read the stories that shaped them. With each perspective shared, users can explore commonalities and form deeper connections.

fields.title: Bandly
fields.description: As an undergrad design student, I developed a patented process that turns real wood into a super strong & flexible bendable band material. The goal here is to merge a bit of nature to enhance your tech. You shouldn't have to look trade style for technology.

fields.title: MAXTAND
fields.description: The attractive arm stand is rated for up to 88lbs of weight, but it can easily handle much more than that judging by the guy sitting on it. It will not only raise gear up as high as 15" off any surface, but it also offer as many 18 different resting positions.
